  "title": "Dietetic Technician (GOVT/MEDICAL) - Entry Level/West/Office Hours #HAO",
  "description": "<p>Salary: up to $3000</p><p>Working Days & Hours: Mon-Fri Office Hours</p><p>Location: Queenstown</p><p>Job Description:</p><p></p><p>•       Assist manager in administration work and nutrition-related matters.</p><p></p><p>•       Assist in development of nutritional education material.</p><p></p><p>•       Write minutes and reports.</p><p></p><p>•       Update Dietetics Web page.</p><p></p><p>•       Participate in Quality Improvement Projects.</p><p></p><p>•       Assist dietitian in setting up nutrition education programs.</p><p></p><p>•       Assist dietitian in the development of slides for nutrition education.</p><p></p><p>•       Assist dietitian in internal / external departmental projects.</p><p></p><p>•       Assist dietitian in nutritional analysis using computer software.</p><p></p><p>•       Assist in appointment booking for patients.</p><p></p><p>•       Perform & document pre-clerking of patients, including social, medical, weight history, diet history, food frequency questionnaire, as needed.</p><p>•       Manage oral nutrition supplements (ONS) samples, ensuring no expired products, proper storage and tracking of samples.</p><p>•       Answer phone calls, handling enquiries, recording and conveying messages.</p><p></p><p>•       Assist with data entry in research.</p><p></p><p>•       Expand Food Composition Database.</p><p></p><p>•       Collate weekly and monthly statistics.</p><p></p><p>•       Provide reminders for patients who missed appointments.</p><p></p><p>•       Assist dietitian in community outreach programmes and research.</p><p></p><p>Job Requirements: Min Diploma in Food Science or similar</p><p>Interested candidates, please submit your resume to: allylok@recruitexpress.com.sg</p><p>Ally Audrey Lok Xin Woon</p><p>Recruit Express Pte Ltd (Healthcare & Lifescience)</p><p>Company EA Licence number : 99C4599</p><p>Personnel EA License: R21102307</p><p><a href=\"mailto:allylok@recruitexpress.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">allylok@recruitexpress.com.sg</a><a href=\"mailto:allylok@recruitexpress.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"></a></p>",
